>wait
>wait
>wait

When you are returned at last to the Vogon Hold, type the password on the keyboard, enclosed in quotes (i.e. type "venchit"). Get the atomic vector plotter and your gown and towel. Wait a couple of turns. You will be rudely hustled into the airlock. Examine the Thumb and you will see blinkenlights. (Alles lookenspeepers!) Press the green button to hitch a ride aboard a spaceship whose occupants are not about to violently eject you into space.

>type "venchit" on keyboard
>take atomic vector plotter
>take gown
>take towel
>wait
>examine thumb
>press green button

Wait four turns until "hearing" disappears, then listen to the dark. Try to go port four times, and the game will tell you the exit is actually aft, so go aft to Entry Bay Number Two. Read the brochure. You will follow Ford to the ship's Bridge. Wait twice.

