>put rasp in thing
>put pliers in thing

Take the Improbability Drive. Go fore twice and up to the Bridge. Drop the drive and the cup of ATS (If you're told you don't have all those things, wait a turn or two for the thing to catch up to you from dropping it in the drive room). Put the small plug on the drive into the small receptacle on the plotter. Put the long, dangly bit of the plotter (you can refer to it just as "bit") in the cup. Turn on the Improbability Drive and you will find yourself in the Dark.

>take improbability drive
>go fore
>go fore
>go up
>wait
>drop drive
>drop cup
>put small plug into plotter
>put bit in cup
>turn on improbability drive

Wait four turns and smell the dark. Examine the shadow and you'll find out that you're back with the Vogons, who will blast you back into space. Wait four turns again and hear the dark. To return to the dark, go aft twice, the port, then starboard, and then up to the bridge. Turn on the improbability drive and wait four turns again.

