Touch the Dark, and drink the liquid. In this scene you're at the Islington party where Trillian hooked up with Zaphod in the first place. Examine Arthur. Drop the wine, and get the fluff from his jacket. Open your bag, put in the fluff, and then pick up the wine again. Now that you have the fluff, you can just wait while Arthur bores you until Phil comes and picks you up, and you'll be left in the Dark again. Wait four turns, hear the dark, and go aft, aft, and up to the Bridge. Put the seat cushion fluff in your gown. If your load becomes too heavy and or there are too many items in the thing, remove from the thing and then drop the sales brochure and the towel. Open the handbag and get the tweezers and fluff.

