Go down and aft to Corridor, Aft End. Try to go port and you will be told the "screening door" is closed, so open it. Since you are intelligent enough to have both tea and no tea, it will open for you. Drink the tea, then go port into Marvin's Pantry. Drop thing and then get the chisel and the paint chipper. Say Marvin, open the hatch. Go starboard and down to the Hatchway. Eat the fruit. Drop everything but the tool you saw yourself giving to Marvin. (You can be wearing your gown, but you need to drop the thing). If you dropped the paint chipper, pick it up again. 

